				<wikidot:authorName>Montala</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1569861</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>Additionally, use of SCP-1711-3 may cause moderate-to-severe stomachaches, headaches, mild fever, vomiting and dry heaves, and sleeping disorders for a period of 2-6 weeks following its use</p> </blockquote> <p>This right here sealed my upvote. Use of an abnormally <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">long</span> severe (was the word I meant, my bad)list of side-effects as if from a commercial seriously in an SCP article? <em>Brilliant.</em> However,</p> <blockquote> <p>Speaking in a language no one else can understand wasn't all that it was cut out to be, wasn't it?</p> </blockquote> <p>Should the second &quot;wasn't&quot; be &quot;was?&quot; &quot;Speaking in a language no one else can understand wasn't all that it was cut out to be, was it?&quot;</p> <p>+1 for a job well done.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
